OL,7,FTwo inmates have died at Bridgend's
OL,8,FParc Prison, bringing the total
OL,9,Ffatalities to nine in two months.
OL,11,FA HMP Parc spokesperson confirmed the
OL,12,Fdeaths of 73-year-old David Maggs and
OL,13,F19-year-old Michael Horton on Tuesday,
OL,14,F7 May.
